#: ../../../admin-guide/initrd.rst:348
msgid ""
"Note that the mechanism is incompatible with NFS and similar file systems."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/initrd.rst:351
msgid ""
"This old, deprecated mechanism is commonly called ``change_root``, while the "
"new, supported mechanism is called ``pivot_root``."
